title: #92Noon! Levine/Clomp/Leber/Birk
description: Wild win last night! Then GM Thad Levine joins ahead of Twins home opener and Ryan Cardinal's Country Clomp finishes the first hour with college hockey. Leber and Birk make their respective weekly appearances, and the show wraps with a Whistle Stop journey to Chaska!
